headline: The SEC Can Learn From the IRS in Making Regulation Simpler for Crypto
summary: The IRS has relied on voluntary disclosure programs to bring taxpayers into compliance rather than imposing punitive actions upfront. A similar model should be applied to crypto regulation as well, says Miles Fuller, Director of Government Solutions, TaxBit.
